title: Add the location 23,74 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x24dfdd0402086d665dafec765008b6bc1af768a6 (JDnft)

## NFT Art Gallery

![NFT Art Gallery](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/23/74/map.png)

Should the scene located at 23,74 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

All Time High Art Gallery - a great place to see unique crypto art, discover new artists, and share your work with the community. Founded in December 2020, and regularly updated with new work on display.

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=34d64450-e19b-11eb-a20f-d75df7f87ed8)**
